\beta
p_i(x)=p_i(x_0)+\int_{x_0}^x h_i(t)\,dt \tag1
x\in [\alpha,\beta)
x_0=\alpha
p_i(\alpha)=0
x\in [\beta,\gamma)
x_0=\gamma
p_i(\gamma)=\int_{\alpha}^\gamma h_i=0
p_i(x)=\int_{\gamma}^x -1\,dt = \gamma-x
q_i
x\in [\alpha,\beta)
x_0=\alpha
q_i(\alpha)=0
x\in [\beta,\gamma)
x_0=\gamma
q_i(\gamma)=\int_{\alpha}^\gamma p_i=\frac12((\alpha-\beta)^2+(\beta-\gamma)^2)
q_i(x)=q_i(x_0)+\int_{x_0}^x p_i(t)\,dt \tag2
